high_descs: Walk to the sidetable on the left.
Pick up the yellow knife from the nightstand.
Turn left to exit the room and reach the lemon across the passage on the right.
Cut the nearest lemon into slices on the sink with the knife.
Put the knife on the sink.
Take a slice of lemon from the sink.
Turn left to walk down the passage and turn right at the shelf to reach the sidetable with the microwave.
Put the lemon on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the slice of Lemon on the SideTable.

high_descs: Go to the sidetable ahead and to the left.
Pick up the knife off the bedstand.
Exit the room through the doorway to the left of the bedstand, then go ahead into the bathroom.
Slice the nearest lemon on the bathroom sink.
Place the knife down on the sink.
Pick up a slice of lemon from the plate.
Turn around and go right and straight into the next room, then right again towards the sidetable.
Place the lemon on the sidetable in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice a Lemon and place one slice on a SideTable.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the side table.
Pick up knife from the side table.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the desk.
Place lemon on the desk.
Head straight towards the sink by turning around and turning left.
Pick up lemon from the side table.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the side table.
Place lemon on the side table.
anns.task_desc: washing lemon and placing it on table.
